{"type": "article", "id": 13052, "title": "趣味帐篷", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-05T07:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000233G4eJTdkK8SF9INZE.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t露营这么有趣的事情，怎么能忍受得了帐篷们一成不变的黑脸，灰脸和绿脸？英国帐篷设计品牌 FieldCandy 推出了一系列有趣的帐篷，有大西瓜块儿，有两只羊，有蜗牛，还有亲吻的情侣。帐篷可以容纳 2-3 个人，有外部抗紫外线设计以及防水等基本功能。帐篷售价 295 美元（约合 1800 元人民币）起，这是<a href=\"http://www.fieldcandy.com/tents/original-explorer\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。同时，帐篷提供定制化服务，<a href=\"http://www.fieldcandy.com/tents/original-explorer/fully-booked.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以定制属于你独一无二的图案。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140705DpUXwNtmr4IAuVqF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140706dN6TRiDbPJIH70qc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140706UWmnpSXxZDwt0C2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140707CmcldqV6jgDX9IaU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140709qYM9Zb86r2sQBajH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140709w6Oe3S012lWFE9TC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140710WbyBPHNliYcGMSpV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140710LVuDEgROw37AvpkY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140711g3kGjuzKAfWCw2Vi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}